tlegills and milkcaps with orange milk.With more than 400 stunning colour photographs and more than forty black-and-white illustrations, this book will enhance the experience of every mushroom forager and wild-table chef.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCooking (Mushrooms). 0aEdible mushroomszEurope, NorthernvIdentification. 0aEdible mushroomszGreat BritainvIdentification. 0aEdible mushrooms-Identification. 7aNATURE / Plants / Mushrooms.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2023 Englishz978311131921608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2023z9783111318615oZDB-23-DPM08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertPrinceton University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023z978311074974808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUIUC Life Sciences 2023 eBook packagez978311123611740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9780691245362?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780691245362423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780691245362/original  a978-3-11-074974-8  Princeton University Press Complete eBook-Package 2023b2023  a978-3-11-123611-7  UIUC Life Sciences 2023 eBook packageb2023  a978-3-11-131921-6  EBOOK PACKAGE Medicine and Life Sciences 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_EMB  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DPMb2023